VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (Environment\.getExternalStorageDirectory|Context\.getExternalFilesDir)\s*\(\)\s*\.write
WHEN EXPR MISSING:EncryptedFile|AES|encrypt|cipher|KeyStore && MISSING:test|example|sample
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects writing to external storage without proper validation or encryption.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Insecure External Storage Write.
